    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎥 <strong>直播还是尖叫？</strong> 👻</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >化身一名无所畏惧的主播——始终隐藏在一张马头面具后——在**《闹鬼主播》**（HAUNTED STREAMER）中探索日本最恐怖的废墟。这是一款单人恐怖体验，每一个诡异瞬间都将被现场直播。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你会获得名声和财富，还是变成又一个失踪者？<br>是时候开始你的直播了。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>捕捉恐怖</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >幽灵、复仇的怨灵和闹鬼现象在黑暗中潜伏。<br>你的任务？ <strong>拍下所有的一切。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >镜头越近，拍摄的时间越长，你的观众就会越多。<br>用最惊悚的内容赚取<strong>点赞</strong>和<strong>超级币</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但请小心……有些东西最好不要看到。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234690/extras/1a920c0809dd1181f1f9af3c39444eb1.poster.avif?t=1751685059\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234690/extras/1a920c0809dd1181f1f9af3c39444eb1.webm?t=1751685059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234690/extras/1a920c0809dd1181f1f9af3c39444eb1.mp4?t=1751685059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>理智 vs. 成功</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你深入得越深，遭遇的恐怖就越可怕。<br>你的理智不会永远保持清醒。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >目睹太多超自然现象会让你的精神崩溃。<br>如果你的理智降到零……<strong>死亡在等着你。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了完美的镜头，你愿意走多远？<br>你能在恐惧和名声之间找到平衡，还是会被疯狂吞噬？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234690/extras/f6a63d0b11c24aa4c45ca9b0036c114b.poster.avif?t=1751685059\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234690/extras/f6a63d0b11c24aa4c45ca9b0036c114b.webm?t=1751685059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234690/extras/f6a63d0b11c24aa4c45ca9b0036c114b.mp4?t=1751685059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>超级币挑战</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的观众渴望危险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在你的直播过程中，观众会<strong>实时</strong>发送挑战任务。<br>完成挑战即可获得高额打赏……但代价是什么？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有些挑战无伤大雅，而另一些……可能会让你丧命。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234690/extras/15d4f37d56ac616a689aebfd1e85d5d0.poster.avif?t=1751685059\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234690/extras/15d4f37d56ac616a689aebfd1e85d5d0.webm?t=1751685059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234690/extras/15d4f37d56ac616a689aebfd1e85d5d0.mp4?t=1751685059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>直播与内容创作政策</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您可以直播并使用本游戏创作可盈利内容。</p>",
